# BuildKit honours <dockerfile>.dockerignore next to the Dockerfile. Patterns
# are relative to the build context (storm-dist/binary/final-package/target),
# so we exclude everything and re-include only the tarball the Dockerfile ADDs.
# This keeps the build context to ~the tarball instead of the whole target dir
# (which also holds the .zip and the extracted distribution).
*
!apache-storm-*.tar.gz
